(3922, 1, '2016-03-21 15:56:50', '2016-03-21 06:56:50', '<p style="text-align: center;">안녕하세요 미스터 엘입니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">대한아이스하키협회의 공식 물류 파트너 DHL이</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">이번에는 대한민국 남자 아이스하키 국가대표팀의 팀 장비를 덴마크로 운송했습니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">자세한 소식 사진으로 만나보세요^^</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3917" src="http://dhlkorea.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/DHL아이스하키1-1.jpg" alt="DHL아이스하키1" width="740" height="362" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">국제특송 DHL코리아가 ‘2016 남자 유로아이스하키 챌린지컵’에 참가하는 대한민국 남자 아이스하키 국가대표팀의</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">공식 유니폼, 하키스틱, 스케이트, 보호장구 등 약 1톤 가량의 장비를 개최지인 덴마크 코펜하겐으로 운송했습니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3919" src="http://dhlkorea.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/DHL아이스하키3.jpg" alt="DHL아이스하키3" width="740" height="424" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3920" src="http://dhlkorea.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/DHL아이스하키4.jpg" alt="DHL아이스하키4" width="740" height="378" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">DHL코리아는 작년 여름 대한아이스하키협회와 파트너십을 체결한 후,</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">항공 및 통관 서비스를 비롯해 국가대표팀이 세계 각지에서 경기를 펼치는데 필요한 모든 물류 서비스를 전담하고 있습니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">이번 2016 유로아이스하키 챌린지컵을 위한 덴마크 운송은</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><u>15/16 시즌 폴란드 유로아이스하키 챌린지컵, 리투아니아 U20 세계선수권 대회에 이은 3</u><u><u>번째 운송</u></u>입니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">또, 올 4월에는 2016 세계 남자 아이스하키 선수권 대회가 열리는 폴란드에 대표팀 개인장비를 포함해 약 1.5톤 이상의 물품을 운반할 예정입니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"> .</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">공식 물류 스폰서 DHL의 빠르고 안전한 배송과</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">2월 8일(월)부터 7일간 진행되는 ‘2016 남자 유로아이스하키 챌린지컵’에 참가하는</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">국가대표 선수들에게도 많은 관심과 응원 부탁 드립니다.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3921" src="http://dhlkorea.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/1._dhl_footer.png" alt="1._dhl_footer" width="740" height="28" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>', '[DHL뉴스]국제특송 DHL코리아, 유로아이스하키 챌린지컵 출전 국가대표팀 팀장비 배송', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '551-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-21 15:56:50', '2016-03-21 06:56:50', '', 551, 'http://dhlkorea.com/wp/2016/03/21/551-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3923, 1, '2016-03-21 15:58:24', '2016-03-21 06:58:24', '', 'KakaoTalk_20160321_143438893', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'kakaotalk_20160321_143438893', '', '', '2016-03-21 15:58:24', '2016-03-21 06:58:24', '', 1118, 'http://dhlkorea.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/KakaoTalk_20160321_143438893.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(3924, 1, '2016-03-21 15:58:54', '2016-03-21 06:58:54', '<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/markjsebastian/">Image Credit</a> It but remains for this council to command, and Tal Hajus must prove his fitness to rule. Were he a brave man he would invite Tars Tarkas to combat, for he does not love him, but Tal Hajus is afraid; Tal Hajus, your jeddak, is a coward. With my bare hands I could kill him, and he knows it."\r\n\r\nAfter I ceased there was tense silence, as all eyes were riveted upon Tal Hajus. He did not speak or move, but the blotchy green of his countenance turned livid, and the froth froze upon his lips. Tal Hajus," said Lorquas Ptomel in a cold, hard voice, "never in my long life have I seen a jeddak of the Tharks so humiliated. There could be but one answer to this arraignment. We wait it." And still Tal Hajus stood as though electrified.<!--more-->\r\n\r\n"Chieftains," continued Lorquas Ptomel, "shall the jeddak, Tal Hajus, prove his fitness to rule over Tars Tarkas?"\r\n\r\nThat decree was final, and so Tal Hajus drew his long-sword and advanced to meet Tars Tarkas. The combat was soon over, and, with his foot upon the neck of the dead monster, Tars Tarkas became jeddak among the Tharks. His first act was to make me a full-fledged chieftain with the rank I had won by my combats the first few weeks of my captivity among them.\r\n\r\nSeeing the favorable disposition of the warriors toward Tars Tarkas, as well as toward me, I grasped the opportunity to enlist them in my cause against Zodanga. I told Tars Tarkas the story of my adventures, and in a few words had explained to him the thought I had in mind.\r\n\r\n"John Carter has made a proposal," he said, addressing the council, "which meets with my sanction. I shall put it to you briefly. Dejah Thoris, the Princess of Helium, who was our prisoner, is now held by the jeddak of Zodanga, whose son she must wed to save her country from devastation at the hands of the Zodangan forces.', '한옥에서의 1박 2일 힐링 여행', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1118-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-21 15:58:54', '2016-03-21 06:58:54', '', 1118, 'http://dhlkorea.com/wp/2016/03/21/1118-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3925, 1, '2016-03-21 16:00:20', '2016-03-21 07:00:20', '오늘도 더 나은 DHL을 위해 힘써주시는 직원여러분,\r\n어느새 봄 기운이 물씬 느껴집니다.\r\n따듯한 봄날 오직 직원 여러분만을 위해서 준비한 한옥에서 즐기는 운치있는 밤에 여러분을 초대합니다.\r\n사랑하는 가족, 연인, 친구, 회사동료와 함께 떠나는 힐링 여행에 신청하고 싶다면, 실명과 신청 이유를 남겨주세요. 한옥 게스트 하우스 숙박권과 한식뷔페 식사권을 드립니다!', '한옥에서의 1박 2일 힐링 여행', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1118-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-21 16:00:20', '2016-03-21 07:00:20', '', 1118, 'http://dhlkorea.com/wp/2016/03/21/1118-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
